    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;To use TLS Encrypted ClientHello (ECH), the client needs to learn the ECH configuration for a server before it attempts a connection to the server.  This specification provides a mechanism for conveying the ECH configuration information via DNS, using a SVCB or HTTPS resource record (RR).&lt;/p&gt;</t>
